				<h3>Do you finance to those with poor credit?</h3>
				<p id="credit">Yes, we have a team of people that will help you get into a new or used car. We first check your credit score to see where you stand. And if it's low then we will adjust to make some sort of payment plan in order to get you on your way.</p>
				<a href="#header">Back to the top</a>
				<h3>What are your operating hours?</h3>
				<p id="hoursofOp">We are open from 10am to 11:30pm, 7 days a week. We are also open on most major holidays except for new years.</p>
				<a href="#header">Back to the top</a>
				<h3>Where can I get a quote?</h3>
				<p id="quote">Give us a call at our toll free <a href="contactus.html">number</a> or stop by at our location and we will gladly help you. We'll give you the best price that satisfies your price budget.</p>
				<a href="#header">Back to the top</a>
				<h3>What is the best way to contact a representative?</h3>
				<p id="representative">If you need more help we have representatives on standby ready to help with any particular questions you may have when it comes to finding a vehicle. So feel free to contact us anytime via email or our 24 hour hotline. Click <a href="contactus.html">here</a> for more info. </p>
				<a href="#header">Back to the top</a>
				<h3 id="employment">Employment Opportunities</h3>
				<p>We provide opportunities for employment. If you love to interact with customers and have a can do attitude attitude then please email us our resume and we'll will get back to you as soon as possible</p>
				<a href="#header">Back to the top</a>

				<h3>Do you provide a history of previous ownership for used cars?</h3>
				<p id="history">We are partnered with Kelley Bluebook and Carfax so that way you can get the most accurate information from the history of the used cars. Such as mileage usage, the number of previous owners, and if the car has been in an accident.</p>
				<a href="#header">Back to the top</a>
				<h3>Carworld Forum</h3>
				<p id="forum">Have questions? Join our CarWorld Forums today, where you can meet and interact with other CarWorld customers. Find out about car meets or special events in your area.</p>
				<a href="#header">Back to the top</a>
				<h3>Newsletter</h3>
				<p id="news">Sign up for our weekly newsletter to find about upcoming events and promotions. Our newsletter is a great way to keep up with events and also showcases customers' cars. Keep an eye out for giveaways and sweepstakes by our sponsors!</p>
